      "Drawer often uses DrawerContent + DrawerHeader + DrawerBody + DrawerFooter"
    ],
    "state_patterns": [
      "Select/Input/Textarea are usually controlled.",
      "Modal/Drawer use boolean isOpen + onClose.",
      "Tabs can be uncontrolled via defaultActive or observed with onTabChange."
    ]
